<html>
	<head>
		<title>HTML CONCEPTS</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
		
		<script src="script.js"></script>
		
	</head>
	
	<body>
		<h1 id="heading">HTML CONCEPTS</h1>
		
		<h2>1. html text formatting</h2> 
		<div>
			<p>normal text - this is a sample paragraph.</p>
			
			<p>
				1. bold - <b>this is a sample paragraph.</b>
			</p>
			
			<p>
				2. italic - <i>this is a sample paragraph.</i>
			</p>
			
			<p>
				3. strikethorugh - <strike>this is a sample paragraph.</strike>
			</p>
			
			<p>
				4. underline - <u>this is a sample paragraph.</u>
			</p>
			
			<hr />
			
			<p>
				5. strong (similar to bold) - <strong>this is a sample paragraph.</strong>
			</p>
			
			<p>
				6. emphasized -(similar to italic) - <em>this is a sample paragraph.</em>
			</p>
			
		</div>
		
